---
title: Matar Paneer Curry with Green Peas and Yellow Potato
description: Paneer is a fresh semi-firm cheese commonly used in South Asian cuisine. Its mild flavour complements this spicy curry sauce perfectly! Coupled with tender green peas, this delicious dish makes the perfect vegetarian meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/matar-paneer-curry-d55b3cd3.jpg
